Stretched box concept (C2).  Examples from the ceder chest.

sdr> /program = C2
C2
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.RH_COLUMN)
| 1B^  1Gv
| 
| 2B^  2Gv
| 
| 4G^  4Bv
| 
| 3G^  3Bv
sdr> stretched box counter rotate 1/4
| 4G>  1B>
| 
| 4B<  1G<
| 
| 3G>  2B>
| 
| 3B<  2G<
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.RH_TIDAL_LINE)
| 1B^  1G^  2B^  2G^  4Gv  4Bv  3Gv  3Bv
sdr> stretched line cross fire
| 4G^  1Bv  3G^  2Bv
| 
| 4B^  1Gv  3B^  2Gv
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.LH_TIDAL_WAVE)
| 1Bv  1G^  2Bv  2G^  4Gv  4B^  3Gv  3B^
sdr> stretched wave recycle
| 4Bv  4Gv  3Bv  3Gv
| 
| 1G^  1B^  2G^  2B^
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.RH_TIDAL_LINE)
| 1B^  1G^  2B^  2G^  4Gv  4Bv  3Gv  3Bv
sdr> face in
| 1B>  1G>  2B>  2G>  4G<  4B<  3G<  3B<
sdr> stretched column dixie style to a wave
| 4Gv  1B^  4Bv  1G^  3Gv  2B^  3Bv  2G^
sdr> /// compare:
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.LINES_FACING_OUT)
| 1B^  1G^  2B^  2G^
| 
| 4Gv  4Bv  3Gv  3Bv
sdr> stretched box shakedown
| 4G>  1B<  4B>  1G<
| 
| 3G>  2B<  3B>  2G<
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.LINES_FACING_OUT)
| 1B^  1G^  2B^  2G^
| 
| 4Gv  4Bv  3Gv  3Bv
sdr> stretch shakedown
| 4G>  3G>  1B<  2B<
| 
| 4B>  3B>  1G<  2G<
sdr> /// compare:
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.RH_TIDAL_WAVE)
| 1B^  1Gv  2B^  2Gv  4G^  4Bv  3G^  3Bv
sdr> stretched wave ah so
| 1G^  1Bv  2G^  2Bv
| 
| 4B^  4Gv  3B^  3Gv
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.RH_TIDAL_WAVE)
| 1B^  1Gv  2B^  2Gv  4G^  4Bv  3G^  3Bv
sdr> stretch ah so
| 1G^  4B^  1Bv  4Gv
| 
| 2G^  3B^  2Bv  3Gv
sdr> /exit
